Title: No horizons in pp-waves
Authors: Veronika E Hubeny and Mukund Rangamani
Comments: 19 pages, 1 figure, uses harvmac and epsf
Report-no: SU-ITP-02/40, UCB-PTH-02/48, LBNL-51675
Journal-ref: JHEP 0211 (2002) 021
\\
  We argue that pp-wave backgrounds can not admit event horizons. We also
comment on pp-wave generalizations which would admit horizons and show that
there exists a black string solution which asymptotes to a five dimensional
plane wave background.
